nscde-wayland (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * CDE-style front panel (nscde-panel)
  * Control center (nscde-control-center) with Sysinfo, DefaultApps,
    Backdrop, Color, Font, and Window manager pages
  * Session dialog (nscde-wayland-logout)
  * Theme generation for labwc, GTK4, Kvantum, Firefox
  * XDG menu generation
  * Display scaling support

